metadata.name: Dancing Korean pines #1
metadata.description: Korean Pine is a unique type of pine. A gently dancing tree, Korean Pine is found on hikes throughout the Korean mountains, and has been regularly featured in traditional Korean art, especially from the Joseon period. These elegant Korean Pines growing on rocky soil often symbolize the perseverance and resilience of the Korean people. This pine is just above 10 million people in the city of Seoul.
